<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Do not be like a horse or like a mule, which have no understanding;</para>

<para style="q1">it is only with bridle and bit to control them</para>

<para style="q1">that they will go where you want them to.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />The wicked have many sorrows,</para>

<para style="q1">but Yahweh's covenant faithfulness will surround the one who trusts in him.</para>
